ding__UoDnH">LARB Staff Recommendations</h3><ul class="styles_list__Ts01_ styles_vertical__erkQK" style="--max-columns: 4;"><li class="styles_item__DZs3I"><article class="styles_container__cv7pq"><h2 class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_titleMedium__AhArg styles_titleSmall__BCl3n styles_title__6redl"><a href="/article/rereading-armies-night/">Reading “The Armies of the Night” in an Age of Youth Protest</a></h2><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_dekSmall__CFgz_ styles_dek__96BUv">What Norman Mailer’s 1968 antiwar classic has to say about the amorphousness of contemporary protest.</p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_byline__5upiN"><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom"><a href="/contributor/francis-wade/">Francis Wade</a></span><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom styles_date__ZI0YT">Aug 12, 2019</span></p></article></li><li class="styles_item__DZs3I"><article class="styles_container__cv7pq"><h2 class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_titleMedium__AhArg styles_titleSmall__BCl3n styles_title__6redl"><a href="/article/confessions-of-a-left-conservative-norman-mailer-in-the-library-of-america/">Confessions of a Left-Conservative: Norman Mailer in the Library of America</a></h2><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_dekSmall__CFgz_ styles_dek__96BUv">An essential writer in his quintessential decade.</p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_byline__5upiN"><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom"><a href="/contributor/jonathan-kirshner/">Jonathan Kirshner</a></span><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom styles_date__ZI0YT">Sep 19, 2018</span></p></article></li></ul></section><div class="styles_container__Pn_Qf styles_cta__rFpfQ"><div><h4 class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_headingLarge__iJMBf styles_headingSmall__1SEHV styles_title__i_7lc">Did you know LARB is a reader-supported nonprofit?</h4><hr><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_dekSmall__CFgz_ styles_blurb__1U_Uk"><p>LARB publishes daily without a paywall as part of our mission to make rigorous, incisive, and engaging writing on every aspect of literature, culture, and the arts freely accessible to the public. Help us continue this work with your tax-deductible donation today!</p><br></p></div><div><a color="default" trackingparams="[object Object]" class="styles_container__suoPq styles_tag__A3Le9 styles_color-default__2eVHz styles_medium__M2a_l" href="/donate/"><p class="styles_textWrapper__sbQc7">Donate</p></a></div></div></div></article><aside class="_slug__sidebar__iorkq"><div class="_slug__sidebarInner__7lkDw"><section class="styles_container__kY9OW styles_padded__W_oLw"><ul class="styles_list__Ts01_ styles_vertical__erkQK" style="--max-columns: 4;"><li class="styles_item__DZs3I"><article class="styles_container__cv7pq _slug__donationCard__glcwg styles_full__R_s2s styles_mobile-clear__TIBj_"><div class="styles_imageWrapper___uyRL styles_landscape__G1uEe styles_cardImageWrapper__LLR4l styles_hover__hdwW3"><div class="styles_imageBg__jMneT" style="background-color: rgb(157, 197, 194);"></div><img fetchpriority="high" width="NaN" height="NaN" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="styles_image__wEhq8" sizes="
