rapdoor-of-her-own/">A Trapdoor of Her Own</a></h2><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_byline__5upiN"><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom"><a href="/contributor/emmeline-clein/">Emmeline Clein</a></span><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom styles_date__ZI0YT">Oct 6</span></p></article></li><li class="styles_item__DZs3I"><article class="styles_container__cv7pq"><h2 class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_titleMedium__AhArg styles_titleSmall__BCl3n styles_title__6redl"><a href="/article/the-inconvenient-scholarship-of-kevin-roberts/">The Inconvenient Scholarship of Kevin Roberts</a></h2><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_byline__5upiN"><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom"><a href="/contributor/samuel-g-freedman/">Samuel G. Freedman</a></span><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom styles_date__ZI0YT">Sep 29</span></p></article></li><li class="styles_item__DZs3I"><article class="styles_container__cv7pq"><h2 class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_titleMedium__AhArg styles_titleSmall__BCl3n styles_title__6redl"><a href="/article/moving-towards-life/">Moving Towards Life</a></h2><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_byline__5upiN"><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom"><a href="/contributor/marina-magloire/">Marina Magloire</a></span><span class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_author__oKZom styles_date__ZI0YT">Aug 7</span></p></article></li></ol></section><div class="styles_container__oYcmu styles_margin__brAgU"><div class="adunitContainer"><div class="adBox" id="adSlot-0" style="" data-google-query-id="CMfQnuSqo4kDFQWFrgUdfSUcag"><div id="google_ads_iframe_6263889/larb-v2-article-square-1_0__container__" style="border: 0pt none;"><iframe id="google_ads_iframe_6263889/larb-v2-article-square-1_0" name="google_ads_iframe_6263889/larb-v2-article-square-1_0" title="3rd party ad content" width="300" height="2