A9GU"><a title="Facebook" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="styles_socialIcon__1YYCC" href="https://www.facebook.com/lareviewbooks/"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 32" class="styles_socialLogo__vH0sH"><path fill="#DEFEF6" d="M4.726 32V17.405H0v-5.688h4.726V7.52C4.726 2.652 7.589 0 11.775 0c2 0 3.725.157 4.225.226v5.086h-2.902c-2.271 0-2.712 1.12-2.712 2.768v3.63h5.423l-.704 5.688h-4.72v14.595h-5.66z"></path></svg></a><a title="Twitter" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="styles_socialIcon__1YYCC" href="https://twitter.com/lareviewofbooks"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 32 26" class="styles_socialLogo__vH0sH"><path fill="#DEFEF6" d="M32 3.08a13 13 0 0 1-3.774 1.03A6.58 6.58 0 0 0 31.115.482a13.1 13.1 0 0 1-4.168 1.592A6.55 6.55 0 0 0 22.159 0a6.56 6.56 0 0 0-6.565 6.562q0 .773.169 1.496A18.64 18.64 0 0 1 2.237 1.206a6.552 6.552 0 0 0 2.028 8.758 6.5 6.5 0 0 1-2.97-.82v.08a6.57 6.57 0 0 0 5.263 6.434 6.46 6.46 0 0 1-2.97.113 6.58 6.58 0 0 0 6.132 4.56 13.16 13.16 0 0 1-8.151 2.806c-.531 0-1.054-.032-1.569-.088A18.6 18.6 0 0 0 10.058 26c12.07 0 18.675-9.996 18.675-18.666 0-.281 0-.563-.016-.852a13.4 13.4 0 0 0 3.275-3.394"></path></svg></a><a title="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="styles_socialIcon__1YYCC" href="https://instagram.com/lareviewofbooks"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 29 30" class="styles_socialLogo__vH0sH"><path fill="#DEFEF6" d="M26.587.5H2.42A2.42 2.42 0 0 0 0 2.921V27.08A2.42 2.42 0 0 0 2.421 29.5H26.58A2.42 2.42 0 0 0 29 27.079V2.92A2.42 2.42 0 0 0 26.579.5zm-6.135 4.34c0-.642.526-1.176 1.168-1.176h3.497a1.18 1.18 0 0 1 1.176 1.176v3.395a1.18 1.18 0 0 1-1.176 1.176H21.62a1.174 1.174 0 0 1-1.168-1.176zm-5.716 3.798a6.34 6.34 0 0 1 0 12.678 6.345 6.345 0 0 1-6.343-6.335c0-3.504 2.839-6.336 6.343-6.343m11.766 18.364H2.506V12.76h3.682a8.7 8.7 0 0 0-.294 2.22 8.844 8.844 0 0 0 8.842 8.841c4.881 0 8.842-3.96 8.842-8.841 0-.766-.109-1.509-.294-2.22h3.21V27z"></path></svg></a><a title="YouTube" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="styles_socialIcon__1YYCC" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/LARBeditorial"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 37 26" class="styles_socialLogo__vH0sH"><path fill="#DEFEF6" d="m14.68 7.409 9.995 5.216-9.994 5.176zM18.489 0S10.728 0 5.55.37c-.726.09-2.3.098-3.71 1.565C.733 3.064.37 5.61.37 5.61S0 8.602 0 11.593V14.4c0 2.99.371 5.982.371 5.982s.363 2.547 1.468 3.668c1.412 1.475 3.259 1.427 4.082 1.58 2.96.282 12.575.371 12.575.371s7.776-.008 12.954-.387c.726-.089 2.3-.097 3.71-1.564 1.106-1.12 1.469-3.668 1.469-3.668S37 17.39 37 14.399v-2.806c0-2.99-.371-5.982-.371-5.982s-.363-2.547-1.468-3.668C33.757.468 32.176.46 31.45.379 26.27 0 18.503 0 18.503 0z"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class="styles_infoDescriptionColumn__erLyZ"><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_body__LwT3a styles_aboutText__K6RRD">The Los Angeles Review of Books is a nonprofit organization dedicated to promoting and disseminating rigorous, incisive, and engaging writing on every aspect of literature, culture, and the arts.</p></div><div class="styles_infoLinksColumn__atfwe"><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/masthead/">Masthead</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/supporters/">Supporters</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/get-involved/">Volunteer</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/newsletter/">Newsletter</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/press-center/">News &amp; Press</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/shop/">Shop</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/contact/">Contact</a></p><p class="styles_text__Q5ZIK text styles_footer__M2jTK"><a href="/about/privacy/">Privacy Policy<